          <p class="card-text">Admin members - Staff, Security,
            Management and Board Members LogIn here. Login using
            your Staff Code and Password to access your account,
            keep track of your work and other official services.
          </p>
          <a href="/adminHome" target='_blank' class="btn
            btn-primary btnone">Log In</a>
        </div>
      </div>
